    <h1 class="text-center mb-4">Common Gynecological Issues</h1>
    <p class="text-center mb-5">Understanding, preventing, and treating common gynecological conditions that affect women's health.</p>
    
    <div class="row align-items-center">
      <div class="col-lg-6">
        <h2>About Gynecological Health</h2>
        <p>Gynecological health encompasses the well-being of the female reproductive system, including the uterus, ovaries, fallopian tubes, and breasts. Throughout their lives, many women will experience gynecological conditions that may affect their physical comfort, emotional well-being, and quality of life.</p>
        <p>While some gynecological symptoms can be embarrassing to discuss, it's important to remember that these conditions are common and treatable. Early diagnosis and proper management can prevent complications and improve outcomes.</p>
        <p>This guide covers some of the most common gynecological issues, their symptoms, causes, and treatment options. Always consult with a healthcare provider for personalized medical advice and treatment.</p>
